</span><b>Pricing</b><span class="acssf62a8">: $20 – $50/month | Free plan available | 14-day free trial</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">If you’ve been searching for a profit-tracking app with sufficient tracking features, Profitario won’t let you down. Profitario seamlessly </span><b>integrates with Facebook and Google ads channels, shipping platforms like ShipStation, EasyShip, and the marketplace AliExpress</b><span class="acssf62a8"> to pull your income and expenses from multiple sources.</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">Though</span><b> the integrations are still limited (only Facebook and Google ads)</b><span class="acssf62a8">, if you run ads heavily on these two channels, the Profitario might be suitable for your needs. The app will automatically track your store’s revenue, expenses, and fees to help you stay updated with your business performance.</span></p> <figure id="attachment_2566" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-2566 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg" alt="Profitario Shopify profit tracker app" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg 1600w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-400x225.jpeg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-Profitario-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-conten