Get Profitario</a></b></p> <h3><b>#7. </b><b>Delirious Profit</b></h3> <p><b>Rating: </b><span class="acssf62a8">4.2 (52+ reviews)<br>
</span><b>Pricing</b><span class="acssf62a8">: $5/month | 7-day free trial</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">If you’re on a tight budget and looking for <strong>an affordable Shopify expense tracking solution</strong>, your search should end with Delirious Profit.</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">Delirious Profit has seamless integration with your Shopify store’s inventory, order data, and the shipping platform ShipStation to give you <strong>detailed incomes, costs, revenue, and profit margin breakdowns by product, time frames</strong>, etc.</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">However, be well-noted that Delirious doesn’t have integrations with ad channels. So this might be a big minus for stores that run ads on multiple platforms. However, if you want to have deeper insights than what Shopify’s basic profit reports offer, Delirious should be fine.</span></p> <figure id="attachment_2567" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-2567 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg" alt="Delirious Shopify profit tracker app" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg 1600w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-400x225.jpeg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-Delirious-Profit-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-800x450.jp