th one-time and recurring</span></li> </ul> <p><b><a href="https://apps.shopify.com/profit" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" class="acss2f8ef">Get Delirious Profit</a></b></p> <h3><b>#8. </b><b>Accountify</b></h3> <p><b>Rating: </b><span class="acssf62a8">4.4 (45+ reviews)<br>
</span><b>Pricing</b><span class="acssf62a8">: $11.90/month | Free plan available</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">Accountify is another cost-efficient business profit tracker you should definitely give a shot. With Accountify’s robust tracking features and</span><b> integrations with ad platforms like Facebook, Google, TikTok, and Snapchat</b><span class="acssf62a8">, the app will provide you with an accurate view of your store key statistics. </span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">What’s nice about Accountify is that the app will give you deeper insights into income, expenses, and profit margins per product or order. Another cool stuff is </span><b>Accountify’s revenue distribution map</b><span class="acssf62a8"> which shows you where your revenue mostly comes from.</span></p> <figure id="attachment_2568" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-2568 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg" alt="Accountify Shopify profit tracker app" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg 1600w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-400x225.jpeg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/9-Accountify-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1400x788.jpeg 1400w" layout="intrinsi