</b></p> <h3><b>#9. </b><b>Polar Analytics</b></h3> <p><b>Rating: </b><span class="acssf62a8">5.0 (67+ reviews)<br>
</span><b>Pricing</b><span class="acssf62a8">: $300/month | Free plan available | 14-day free trial</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">And last but certainly not least, Polar Analytics deserves to be the best app for profit and loss, on par with top Shopify profit tracker apps like TrueProfit. </span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">With extensive integration with big ad platforms and top Shopify apps, Polar Analytics will give you the most comprehensive and valuable insights, </span><b>from your profits and losses to detailed breakdowns of your ROAS, repeat purchase rate, lifetime value, etc</b><span class="acssf62a8">. What’s incredible is that you can easily create custom reports that only display the metrics that matter to you.</span></p> <figure id="attachment_2569" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-2569 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg" alt="Polar Analytics Shopify profit tracker app" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps.jpeg 1600w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-400x225.jpeg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/10-Polar-Analytics-Shopify-Profit-Tracker-Apps-1400x788.jpeg 1400