>Alert for abnormal fluctuations in your ROAS or conversions</span></li> <li aria-level="1" class="acssf62a8"><span class="acssf62a8">A mobile app version to track your profit analytics on the go</span></li> </ul> <p><b><a href="https://apps.shopify.com/polar-analytics" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" class="acss2f8ef">Get Polar Analytics</a></b></p> <h2><b>Final thoughts</b></h2> <p>All in all, to make decisions that truly matter, you have to know your store’s real-time and in-depth analytics. And we hope you can find the tracking solution that helps make your life easier among the top 9 <strong>Shopify profit tracker apps</strong> we’ve compiled.</p> <p class="acss25665"><em>Discover what proper profit-tracking looks like at <a href="https://trueprofit.io/?&amp;utm_source=trueprofit.io&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=hyperlink&amp;utm_content=profit-tracker-apps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">trueprofit.io</a></em></p> </div> <div class="amp-wp-content"><amp-addthis width="320" height="92" data-pub-id="ra-5cc8551aa4f16f5c" data-widget-id="cwgj"></amp-addthis></div>   <div class="amp-wp-content post-pagination-meta"> <div id="pagination"> <div class="next"> <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/shopify-ltv/amp/">4 Steps to Calculate Shopify LTV & 5 Tips to Improve Yours! &raquo;</a> </div> <div class="prev"> <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/amazon-cost-of-goods-sold/amp/"> &laquo; All About Amazon Costs of Goods Sold: Definition &amp; Methods</a> </div> <div class="cb"></div> </div> </div>   </div> <div class="amp-wp-article-header amp-wp-article-category ampforwp-meta-taxonomy "> <div class="amp-wp-meta amp-wp-tax-category"> <span>Categories: </span> <span class="amp-cat-8"><a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/category/ecommerce/amp/" title="eCommerce" > eCommerce</a></span> </div> <div class="amp-wp-meta amp-wp-tax-tag ampforwp-tax-tag"> Tags: <span class="amp-tag-40"><a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/tag/profit-tracker-apps/amp/" >profit tracker 